name.jp: 退魔師コスチューム(男の子用)

description.en: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.ar: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.br: Um terno agourento da terra dos mortos. Os espíritos benevolentes percebem seu senso de moda.
description.cns: 来自死者之地的预兆衣服。 仁慈的灵魂被你的时尚吸引。
description.de: Ein Anzug aus dem Land der Toten, der böse Vorahnungen weckt. Wohlwollende Geister werden auf Ihren Sinn für Mode aufmerksam.
description.fi: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.fil: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.fr: Des symboles démoniaques sont brodés au fil d'or, seul un puissant démon peut s'offrir une telle tenue !
description.id: Setelan Peramal dari tanah kematian. Roh yang baik hati memperhatikan selera fashion Anda.
description.it: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.jp: 死者の国からの予兆のスーツ。慈悲深い精神はあなたのファッション感覚に注意を払います。
description.kr: 죽은 자의 땅에서 온 예감의 양복. 자비로운 영혼이 당신의 패션 감각을 알아 차립니다.
description.nl: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.pl: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.ru: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.sp: Un traje ominoso de la tierra de los muertos. Los espíritus benévolos toman nota de tu sentido de la moda.
description.sw: A foreboding suit from the land of the dead. Benevolent spirits take notice of your sense of fashion.
description.th: ชุดลางสังหรณ์จากดินแดนแห่งความตาย ผู้มีจิตเมตตาจะสังเกตความรู้สึกของแฟชั่น
description.tw: 來自死亡之地的服飾，靈魂都將感受到你的時尚
description.vi: Một bộ đồ mang điềm báo từ vùng đất của người chết. Những linh hồn nhân từ để ý đến gu thời trang của bạn.
